0-01-11T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"為左5大訴求推第10下"},{"pid":"3bfa5f6cde2c27936a0382aa70341d4c98866078","tid":1819993,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"support except point 3 <br />\nu never can fight against full gear POPO<br />\nI dun think we should hv direct conflict with them. Teenagers should not sacrifice like this."},{"pid":"606f12e4137eb76a7c143ae449d56c4d9b083889","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"天琦：只要對準政權既<br />\n我地都應該要試！"},{"pid":"58a9ef36369f81eb0f4740e70dcffcd1f2bd035a","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:53:30.000Z","msg":"推呀 無錯<br />\n我地唔應該咁做<br />\n但我地有得選擇咩？<br />\n你估我地唔想打下機就過一日呀？<br />\n咩都要試！<br />\n推"},{"pid":"9d7020be2b07cb19f1accd1af1ec028b0d3b5ddd","tid":1819993,"uid":264963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"手足 一齊加油啦<br />\n為大義來一起奮抗戰"},{"pid":"2d363195abbc9e9f436f3eb33f5ace0adfac299a","tid":1819993,"uid":146193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"317826f7e4a79d363c44cdc5b0c5d0246e883206","tid":1819993,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=d4edf51c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"fdfa468aff351bebda06c8cfe645b1b4510f26fc","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"我可以勇敢面對所有負面情緒<br />\n請求你地支持呢類型0成本既活動<br />\n好過要年青人被捕<br />\n我敢講 有需要既話<br />\n絕對會再次有人企出黎對抗一個壞左既制度"},{"pid":"408ad807bd5c8369cea0da297aecf0b305a7b6c8","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推得太快 都照推"},{"pid":"ce1fb4e1f927d3723a8972b77a7889a73003b925","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"推 我要流上資訊流通面"},{"pid":"503449599fab7c99f741b01a394f85f9de8e4957","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"想我停？ 唔會呀屌你 推呀<br />\n大大力推呀"},{"pid":"7e5bddff06db5439fe4357eea2d91045b4717bcb","tid":1819993,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"590bb24b7c6ae5b6bb57830a606294297c28e04e","tid":1819993,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"屌 不如spread 上ig?"},{"pid":"0750048e631fd83581c01ba063c1902773014c45","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"一人做多小小 <br />\n0成本呀！<br />\n強效益呀"},{"pid":"e5727397929887cd92dc14a2e0b6b2ff14f00f4a","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"590bb24b7c6ae5b6bb57830a606294297c28e04e","tid":1819993,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"屌 不如spread 上ig?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"咩都得 我支持你"},{"pid":"365354416b0ad76da34b807d4a8f5ca536d1cb18","tid":1819993,"uid":206219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"590bb24b7c6ae5b6bb57830a606294297c28e04e","tid":1819993,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"屌 不如spread 上ig?"